-!- FUNCTION: Has a role in the DNA error-free postreplication repair
    (PRR) pathway. Lacks catalytic activity by itself. The ubc13/spm2
    heterodimer catalyzes the synthesis of non-canonical poly-
    ubiquitin chains that are linked through 'Lys-63'.
-!- SUBUNIT: Heterodimer with ubc13.
-!- SIMILARITY: Belongs to the ubiquitin-conjugating enzyme family.
